{
  "id": "67d3f5ceb9582830af66a187",
  "title": "ど真ん中の「ど」みたいな無くてもいい接頭辞",
  "created": 1741944272,
  "updated": 1775254463,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "67d3f5ceb9582830af66a187",
      "text": "ど真ん中の「ど」みたいな無くてもいい接頭辞",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944272,
      "updated": 1741944272
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5d00f1ffd000017afc9",
      "text": "たとえば、",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944272,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afdd",
      "text": "\tおったまげるの「おっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afde",
      "text": "\tちょん切るの「ちょん」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afdf",
      "text": "\tひん曲げるの「ひん」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe0",
      "text": "\tぶっ倒れるの「ぶっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe1",
      "text": "\tぶち込むの「ぶち」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe2",
      "text": "\tずっこけるの「ずっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe3",
      "text": "\tくっつくの「くっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe4",
      "text": "\tとっ捕まるの「とっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe5",
      "text": "\tふん縛るの「ふん」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe6",
      "text": "\tとっ散らかるの「とっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe7",
      "text": "\tかっ食らうの「かっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe8",
      "text": "\tかっさらうの「かっ」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afe9",
      "text": "\tすっ飛ばすの｢すっ｣",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afeb",
      "text": "なんか法則とかあるのかな？[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944297
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afec",
      "text": " 省略して短くなる語は多いけど、長くなるのはなんでだろう",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944667
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afed",
      "text": " \t[強調]表現？",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944666
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0162a0000000000caa80a",
      "text": " \t\t+1[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775244842,
      "updated": 1775244844
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afee",
      "text": " \t[リズム]感や[テンポ]感がよくなる？",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944666
    },
    {
      "id": "69d016240000000000caa809",
      "text": " \t\t+1[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775244836,
      "updated": 1775244840
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5e80f1ffd000017afef",
      "text": " \t接続する語の一文字目が[口語]で伝わりづらい[子音]？",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944297,
      "updated": 1741944666
    },
    {
      "id": "69d016490000000000caa80b",
      "text": " \t\tずっこけるとすっ飛ばすは寧ろ後の語の一音目（破裂音）のほうがはっきりしない？[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775244873,
      "updated": 1775244929
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfcef70000000000635b88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1775226615,
      "updated": 1775226615
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfcef70000000000635b89",
      "text": "打ちkrす→ぶちkrす→ぶっkrす",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1775226615,
      "updated": 1775226657
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfcf2d0000000000635b8c",
      "text": "掻き食らう→かっくらう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1775226669,
      "updated": 1775226676
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfcf6d0000000000635b8d",
      "text": " ご飯を掻き込むのと同じイメージなのか？少し違うかな？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1775226733,
      "updated": 1775226749
    },
    {
      "id": "67d3f5ef0f1ffd000017aff0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1741944303,
      "updated": 1741944303
    },
    {
      "id": "69d03b64000000000096bffd",
      "text": "ちなみに、「ド級」は英国海軍戦艦ドレッドノートの「ド」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775254372,
      "updated": 1775254442
    },
    {
      "id": "69d03bb1000000000096bfff",
      "text": "\tド級戦艦＝ドレッドノート級戦艦",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775254449,
      "updated": 1775254463
    },
    {
      "id": "69d03b64000000000096bffe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775254372,
      "updated": 1775254372
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfc302000000000026cc14",
      "text": "関連？",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775223555,
      "updated": 1775223557
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfc304000000000026cc16",
      "text": "[語源が謎の形態素]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775223557,
      "updated": 1775223560
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfc304000000000026cc15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775223557,
      "updated": 1775223557
    }
  ]
}